graph LR
    Trainer[Kubeflow Trainer Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Trainer -->|creates JobSets| JobSet[JobSet v0.10.1<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io/v1alpha2<br/>REQUIRED]
    Trainer -->|watches CRDs<br/>creates resources| K8sAPI[Kubernetes v1.29+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Trainer -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano v1.13+<br/>scheduling.volcano.sh<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Trainer -.->|job queueing| Kueue[Kueue/scheduler-plugins<br/>v1alpha1<br/>OPTIONAL]
    Trainer -.->|webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager v1.0+<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    Trainer -->|lifecycle mgmt| ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator<br/>CRD Management]
    Trainer -->|UI integration| Dashboard[RHOAI Dashboard<br/>TrainJob creation UI]
    Trainer -->|metrics export| Monitoring[RHOAI Metrics/Monitoring<br/>PodMonitor scraping]

    %% Integration Points
    Trainer -.->|model storage| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Store trained models<br/>Storage API]
    Trainer -.->|datasets/checkpoints| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Object storage<br/>S3 API]

    %% JobSet creates workloads
    JobSet -->|creates| Jobs[Jobs/Pods<br/>Training Workloads]

    %% Training workloads external access
    Jobs -->|dataset download| S3
    Jobs -->|checkpoint upload| S3
    Jobs -->|pull images| Registry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io/modh/training]
    Jobs -.->|store models| ModelRegistry

    %% Monitoring integration
    Monitoring -->|scrapes| Trainer

    %% Dashboard integration
    Dashboard -->|creates TrainJob CRs| K8sAPI

    %% Styling
    style Trainer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style JobSet fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
